# Draw a pentagon by Techch3
# Clearn Screen
cs
# set the start position.
bk 300
#画五条经线
fd 300  rt 108 repeat 4 [fd 300 bk 300 lt 72] 
#回到起点
fd 300 
#画外围
rt 126 repeat 5[fd 352.67 rt 72]

to PENTAGON :x  bk :x fd :x  rt 108 repeat 4 [fd :x bk :x lt 72] fd :x rt 126 repeat 5 [fd 1.17*:x rt 72] end
Y=2Cos 54
## Option
Option 1 cs repeat 5 [fd 300 bk 300 lt 72] fd 300 rt 126 repeat 5[fd 352.67 rt 72]
